imdb.plot outline: Young Actress/Comedian Brandi Aguilar does sketches and impersonations of celebrities such as Miley Cyrus, Courtney Stodden, girls of the show "16 And Pregnant", and more. She also has her chola character, who gets loud at times and isn't as tough as she thinks she is. Brandi also talks about random things and does video dares by her fans.
imdb.title: Weird Brandi
plot: Quirky and spunky young Actress/Comedian Brandi Aguilar does sketches and impersonations of celebrities and TV shows, as well as her own characters.::Anonymous
